  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[On Play] You may play 2 level 4 or lower Digimon cards
    with [Bagra Army] in their traits from your trash without paying their memory
    costs. All Digimon played by this effect gain \uFF1CBlocker\uFF1E until the end
    of your opponent's turn.[Opponent's Turn] When an effect would trash one of your
    other Digimon's digivolution cards, you may trash this Digimon's digivolution
    cards instead."
